<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GRR - Customer Corner</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="GRR Logo" class="logo">
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/customer-corner">Customer Corner</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="container">
        <section class="customer-section">
            <h1>Customer Corner</h1>

            <div class="support-section">
                <h2>Customer Support</h2>
                <p>We're here to help you with any questions or concerns about our latex products.</p>
                <div class="contact-info">
                    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                    <p>Email: support@grr.com</p>
                    <p>Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
                    <p>Hours: Monday - Friday, 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM EST</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="resources">
                <h2>Resources</h2>
                <div class="resource-grid">
                    <div class="resource-card">
                        <h3>Product Catalog</h3>
                        <p>Browse our complete range of latex products</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn">Download Catalog</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="resource-card">
                        <h3>Technical Specifications</h3>
                        <p>Detailed product specifications and guidelines</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn">View Specs</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="resource-card">
                        <h3>Safety Data Sheets</h3>
                        <p>Safety information for all our products</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn">Access SDS</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-section">
                <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <div class="faq-list">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3>What types of latex products do you offer?</h3>
                        <p>We offer a wide range of natural and synthetic latex products suitable for various industrial
                            applications.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3>How do you ensure product quality?</h3>
                        <p>Our products undergo rigorous quality control testing at every stage of production to meet
                            international standards.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3>What are your shipping options?</h3>
                        <p>We offer worldwide shipping with various options to meet your delivery requirements.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 GRR. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>